snippet.title: X-Plane 11 - Now Even More Powerful
snippet.description:
X-Plane 11: More Powerful. Made Useable.

With a brand new user interface, and a new level of quality in the included aircraft, X-Plane 11 is the upgrade you’ve been hoping for. Check it out in this video!
